be some kind of
honor student, too.

180
00:10:29,125 --> 00:10:32,458
Did everybody but me and
Yuki score a seven hundred?

181
00:10:32,541 --> 00:10:34,916
He's like, super-smart!

182
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:37,125
This is just a thought.

183
00:10:37,208 --> 00:10:38,000
Yeah?

184
00:10:38,083 --> 00:10:39,916
But could it be, the problem.

185
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:43,416
is that you two
are too much alike?

186
00:10:49,583 --> 00:10:52,125
Sorry, it's urgent! I gotta go!

187
00:10:52,708 --> 00:10:54,625
Hey, you can't leave!
We just got here!

188
00:10:54,708 --> 00:10:56,791
I'll make it up
to you next time!

189
00:11:02,541 --> 00:11:04,833
It looks like Satsuki
Kuzuhara is still missing.

190
00:11:04,916 --> 00:11:06,416
She just vanished.

191
00:11:06,500 --> 00:11:07,833
I heard the teachers
were ordered

192
00:11:07,916 --> 00:11:09,416
to keep silent about her.

193
00:11:09,500 --> 00:11:12,375
They're afraid if they discuss
it then the students will worry.

194
00:11:12,458 --> 00:11:13,541
Don't they know.

195
00:11:13,625 --> 00:11:15,958
That makes us worry even more?

196
00:11:16,041 --> 00:11:18,250
The chief selling point of this
school is that they keep girls

197
00:11:18,333 --> 00:11:21,500
of a susceptible age isolated
from society, locked away

198
00:11:21,583 --> 00:11:22,916
in this conservatory
environment,

199
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:25,500
to prevent our Psycho-Passes
from getting cloudy.

200
00:11:25,583 --> 00:11:28,000
That's why they sweep all
the problems under the rug.

201
00:11:28,083 --> 00:11:31,625
And besides, they have to keep
up appearances for our parents.

202
00:11:31,708 --> 00:11:33,416
Oh no. I'm scared!

203
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:35,750
If you think that's bad,
listen to this rumor.

204
00:11:35,833 --> 00:11:37,333
Apparently, one of the teachers

205
00:11:37,416 --> 00:11:40,375
who taught here a
few years ago. He was...

