207
00:11:42,708 --> 00:11:45,250
It's Rikako!

208
00:11:49,791 --> 00:11:54,041
I can't figure it out. Why the
hell is Rikako so popular?

209
00:11:54,125 --> 00:11:56,541
She's pretty and
she's intelligent.

210
00:11:56,625 --> 00:11:58,750
Do you really need me to go on?

211
00:11:58,833 --> 00:12:02,416
Yeah, well something
about that girl scares me.

212
00:12:02,500 --> 00:12:03,750
Why's that?

213
00:12:03,833 --> 00:12:07,875
Her eyes can be
so blank sometimes.

214
00:12:07,958 --> 00:12:12,416
It's as if they're staring far
off into another dimension.

215
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:15,083
Kawarazaki. Shimotsuki.

216
00:12:16,125 --> 00:12:17,000
Oh, hey.

217
00:12:17,083 --> 00:12:18,375
Yes, good afternoon.

218
00:12:18,458 --> 00:12:20,333
Sorry to interrupt
your lunch, girls.

219
00:12:20,416 --> 00:12:22,125
What brings you?

220
00:12:22,208 --> 00:12:23,666
Well, neither of
you ladies belongs

221
