clubs, am I right?

222
00:12:26,375 --> 00:12:28,583
These days, having a school
that offers club activities,

223
00:12:28,666 --> 00:12:31,291
like Ousou Academy does,
is pretty uncommon.

224
00:12:31,375 --> 00:12:33,125
Really, it's a rare luxury.

225
00:12:33,208 --> 00:12:35,208
It's a shame to
miss out on that.

226
00:12:35,291 --> 00:12:36,625
Are you recruiting us?

227
00:12:36,708 --> 00:12:38,583
You got me. You see,

228
00:12:38,666 --> 00:12:41,208
