of the art club here.

229
00:12:41,291 --> 00:12:44,416
If you're interested,
come see us in our clubroom.

230
00:12:44,791 --> 00:12:46,791
Oh, and Shimotsuki.

231
00:12:46,875 --> 00:12:49,125
I may get a little
lost in thought sometimes

232
00:12:49,208 --> 00:12:51,750
but I can't see
into other dimensions.

233
