243
00:13:44,708 --> 00:13:46,750
Miss Ouryou.

244
00:13:49,166 --> 00:13:53,416
Tell me what happened
in your own words.

245
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:56,375
That man he's
always looking at me

246
00:13:56,458 --> 00:14:01,916
with these disturbing, almost
just like predatory eyes.

247
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:03,500
Every time I go home.

248
00:14:03,583 --> 00:14:08,000
I find traces that
someone's been in my room.

249
00:14:08,083 --> 00:14:11,250
I just can't take it! But...

